  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc7\u0bb7\u0bbf\u0baf \u0baa\u0bcc\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Medicines were supplied to Sri Lanka by Malaysian Buddhist organizations",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Many Buddhist organizations in Malaysia have donated emergency medicine and medical supplies to Sri Lanka to alleviate the shortage of medicines in Sri Lanka.",
        "On 14th June, Karin Keong representing Chi Hui Tang - Kuala Lumpur, Siu Niok Cho representing Yayasan Chin Chew & Best Wishes Foundation Malaysia and Chief Abbot Wen Ju Seng of PLIA & Pho Kuang Shan Malaysia received US$54046.26 worth of pharmaceuticals from the Sri Lankan High Commissioner to Malaysia A They handed over to Chief Marshal Sumangala Dias.",
        "The Deputy High Commissioner was present at the handing over ceremony. Ms. Dilani Weerakoon and Second Secretary (Commerce). Meghalaya Abeykoon was also present."
      ],
